  "title": "Intake Turbo Charge Pipe 50MM BOV Kit for BMW N54 E60 E88 E89 E90 E92 135i 335i 535i Z4 FE591310",
  "handle": "fe591310-intake-turbo-charge-pipe-50mm-bov-kit-for-bmw-n54-e60-e88-e89-e90-e92-135i-335i-535i-z4",
  "description": "<h4>Application</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>2008-2010 BMW E82 Coupe N54 135i</li>\n  <li>2008-2010 BMW E88 Convertible N54 135i</li>\n  <li>2007-2010 BMW E90 Sedan N54 335i / 335xi</li>\n  <li>2006-2010 BMW E91 Touring N54 335i / 335xi</li>\n  <li>2006-2010 BMW E92 Coupe N54 335i / 335xi</li>\n  <li>2008-2010 BMW 535i / 535ix (E60/E61) N54B30 3.0L Turbocharged</li>\n  <li>2009-2016 BMW Z4 sDrive35i / sDrive35is (E89) N54B30 3.0L Turbocharged</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Increased BHP, more efficient airflow from turbo, improved throttle response</li>\n  <li>High-performance blow off valve for street-driven, turbocharged and supercharged vehicles, supporting up to 1800hp per valve</li>\n  <li>CNC machined from 6061 aluminum, each unit features a large 1.98\" (50.5mm) valve with a Viton O-ring clamped in place to prevent sticking</li>\n  <li>Valve stem and guide are Teflon-lubricated and hard anodized for superior wear resistance</li>\n  <li>V-band clamp for clean and simple installation; oversized banjo fitting for faster actuator response</li>\n  <li>Actuator with high-temp silicone Nomex-reinforced diaphragm for extended life</li>\n  <li>Supports up to 35 PSI with alternate spring options</li>\n  <li>100% brand new, never used or installed</li>\n  <li>Accessories in the photos are included</li>\n  <li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Package Included</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>1X High Flow Charge Pipe Hard Kit</li>\n  <li>1X 50mm Style BOV Black</li>\n  <li>1X Silicon Elbow Black</li>\n  <li>2X T-Bolt Clamps</li>\n  <li>1X V-band Clamp</li>\n  <li>Blow Off Valve Kit with replacement spring</li>\n  <li>Other kits as shown in pictures</li>\n</ul>\n",
